Hi Brego. This IS a good movie, so thanks anyway :-), but it is not Rebecca Lord's World Tour (http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0152153 ), it is Rebecca, la signora del desiderio (1992) (http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0145430/).
